<i>as well as a dash of black pepper.</i>

262
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:02,020
Here you go!

263
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:04,860
Enjoy the Sumire Mark Karaage Roll!

264
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:07,740
Wow, it looks really filling!

265
00:14:08,110 --> 00:14:10,240
It's still sizzling!

266
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,740
It looks delicious!

267
00:14:14,660 --> 00:14:16,330
The chicken's really plump and juicy!

268
00:14:16,620 --> 00:14:20,540
The fried chicken is crispy in parts and tender where the sauce has soaked in.

269
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:23,550
The way all the different flavors mingle between the juicy meat,

270
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:25,710
