325
00:16:34,640 --> 00:16:36,520
Try it for yourself, Auntie!

326
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:38,470
It's really good, seriously!

327
00:16:38,470 --> 00:16:39,930
This is none of your business!

328
00:16:39,930 --> 00:16:42,020
And don't call me "Auntie"!

329
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:43,520
They're right, you know.

330
00:16:43,520 --> 00:16:48,480
You let us try your karaage last time.

331
00:16:49,150 --> 00:16:50,780
Why don't you give ours a shot?

332
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,740
Here's one. Dig in!

333
00:17:02,620 --> 00:17:03,790
<i>This wrap...</i>

334
00:17:03,790 --> 00:17:05,120
<i>is made from rice flour!</i>

335
00:17:05,120 --> 00:17:08,460
<i>I see. This is similar to bÃ¡nh xÃ¨o!</i>

336
