443
00:24:14,590 --> 00:24:16,810
Those who know of me call me...

444
00:24:17,810 --> 00:24:19,270
the Alchemist!

445
00:24:20,810 --> 00:24:24,310
I'm the ninth seat of the Tohtsuki Elite Ten,

446
00:24:24,310 --> 00:24:25,730
Eizan Etsuya.

447
00:24:27,730 --> 00:24:32,320
I'll crush you on the best stage possible.

448
00:24:39,990 --> 00:24:42,790
Next time, at Bento Shop Tomitaya... No, wait!

449
00:24:42,790 --> 00:24:44,300
...on <i>Shokugeki no Souma</i>,

450
00:24:44,300 --> 00:24:46,000
the nineteenth dish:

451
00:24:47,110 --> 00:24:48,550
The Chosen One.

452
00:24:49,320 --> 00:24:52,010
It's so delicious, Yukihira-kun!

453
00:24:52,600 --> 00:24:54,840
I'll do my best at work today!

